      "instruction": "<p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Peel and chop your<strong> red onion[s]</strong> into wedges, then separate the layers into petals</p><p>Cut your <strong>orange[s] </strong>in half</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
