            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>cornflour </strong>with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>5 spice </strong>(you'll us the rest later!), your <strong>black sesame seeds </strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>in a large bowl</p><p>Drain, then add your <strong>king prawns</strong> to the bowl and mix together until coated in the sesame batter</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1721750291552-x200.jpg",
