            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the prawns are cooking, combine the juice<strong> </strong>of the <strong>orange[s]</strong>, <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>honey</strong> and <strong>soy sauce</strong> in a small bowl – this is your<strong> orange sauce</strong></p><p>Once the sesame prawns are cooked through, transfer them to a plate and set aside for later, reserve the pan</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-1721750376625-x200.jpg",
