            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>onion petals</strong>, <strong>pepper strips </strong>and <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>5 spice </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Once starting to soften, add the <strong>orange sauce </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until the sauce is beginning to thicken</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
