      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once beginning to thicken, return the<strong> sesame prawns</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min further or until the sauce begins to stick to the prawns – this is your <strong>sesame orange king prawn stir-fry</strong></p>",
